{"tid":2337224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衞稱毋須恐慌 專家敲響警號  變種武肺肆虐 英童恐廣泛中招","createTime":"2020-12-23T06:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T06:59:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac75e9d30a1c16e0492b44a8467f110e35ee3a78","tid":2337224,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:51:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201223/R56OFUEOYFGBRMUVODXTSB7FEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201223%2FR56OFUEOYFGBRMUVODXTSB7FEM%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=45ab9217\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201223%2FR56OFUEOYFGBRMUVODXTSB7FEM%2F&h=3b40c2b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201223/R56OFUEOYFGBRMUVODXTSB7FEM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n世衞稱毋須恐慌 專家敲響警號 <br />\n變種武肺肆虐 英童恐廣泛中招<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎變種病毒在英國極速傳播，觸發全球40多個國家與地區對英國封關，希望能夠將新病毒株擋在國門之外。英國官員形容變種毒株「失控」後，世界衞生組織（WHO）駁斥說法，強調病毒變種是尋常，毋須恐慌。但有專家懷疑，新毒株不只傳播力更高，而且攻擊兒童的能力可能亦提升。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：英法洽恢復貨運 跟車須檢測<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情爆發初期，科學家已發現兒童病例相對較少，但情況或者有變。英國政府「新興呼吸道病毒威脅諮詢小組」（Nervtag）前日指出，病毒今次變種後，改變了進入人體細胞的方式，「兒童或許變得跟成人一樣容易感染病毒」。倫敦帝國學院病毒學專家巴克利提醒說，「可以預期會見到更多兒童染病」。<br />\n<br />\n小組另一成員、倫敦帝國學。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：日議長罕有同時染流感武肺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YcdgY66fDerfoHszecMZnJgMuEk=/3541x2362/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BQ2X2LHV3ZG7JIBUGKUMMRLBQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYcdgY66fDerfoHszecMZnJgMuEk%3D%2F3541x2362%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBQ2X2LHV3ZG7JIBUGKUMMRLBQI.jpg&h=18001a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■倫敦提高防疫級別後西敏橋變得冷清，途人戴上口罩。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料六周內可微調疫苗<br />\n<br />\n但科學家如今是更加肯定變種病毒株在傳播上威力更強。小組主席、牛津大學新興傳染病專家霍爾比說：「我們現在很有把握，新病毒株比起當前英國境內其他病毒株的傳播力是更強。」<br />\n<br />\n變種病毒株的傳播力比舊毒株高至少70%，會否影響現有疫苗效力，成為焦點。德國BioNTech總裁薩欣昨日指，該公司跟輝瑞合作研發的疫苗，能對付變種病毒的「可能性很高」， 。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n莫德納（Moderna）藥廠亦發聲明指，有信心其武肺疫苗有效對抗這變種病毒，會在未來日子進行測試。<br />\n<br />\n近期多國疫情大反彈，對於病毒變種後有更強傳播力，自然憂慮。世衞緊急事故。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Z8AvndfR5g_6w__qIfPCizPvNI4=/1831x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DNK6F5YKJBFDFKYFBHK5R5K73Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZ8AvndfR5g_6w__qIfPCizPvNI4%3D%2F1831x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDNK6F5YKJBFDFKYFBHK5R5K73Q.jpg&h=683b2d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民眾爭相搶購日用品，超市門外大排長龍。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/niTyCKKpNRpWY0Yy-X2lz9dfWZA=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4LYPF6M5NJAW7ANDIOYNYJW2LQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FniTyCKKpNRpWY0Yy-X2lz9dfWZA%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4LYPF6M5NJAW7ANDIOYNYJW2LQ.jpg&h=e81eb7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■專家指，兒童或與成人一樣容易感染變種病毒。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳播速度尚不及水痘<br />\n<br />\n瑞安又指，雖說新毒株傳播力比舊株強，但傳播速度尚不及引發流行性腮腺炎或水痘的病毒。新毒株也未見在其他國家廣傳，暫時只在澳洲、冰島、意大利、荷蘭、丹麥有零星個案，說疫情「嚴重性增加的證據是零」。但他強調對抗武肺不能鬆懈，「我們需要繼續做一直在做的事，或許力度要再加強些，堅持久一些」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社"},{"pid":"c63372e7b04a711a7f0f4e05fa17b84fc6221a44","tid":2337224,"uid":111019,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"世衞稱毋須恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18623ae6d4e31bcc97fe3bef1de6c74ceca995aa","tid":2337224,"uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"中国武漢變種肺炎"},{"pid":"98c92ab074e6a0762315ce098362956c03e4a091","tid":2337224,"uid":189453,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:58:53.000Z","msg":"世衛稱 唔會人傳人<br />\n世衛稱 中國搞得掂<br />\n世衛清 各國無需要封關"},{"pid":"6a57a6c0d1dc2a258fe941373346b1de516a9b81","tid":2337224,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:59:33.000Z","msg":"開始打疫苗都唔惡得好耐啦<br />\n<br />\n不過班人唔注意衞生好難搞<br />\n<br />\n口罩又戴半個<br />\n<br />\n好多鬼佬朝早先沖涼<br />\n<br />\n成間屋都已經係病毒啦"}]}